rows.label: tlk000501_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Wh-what is happening, mo!
There was an explosion on the roof
of that building, mo!

rows.label: tlk000501_02_msg0002
rows.name: Th-this is an unforeseen situation, mo!

rows.label: tlk000501_02_msg0003
rows.name:
If you don't go help soon,
many people will get hurt, mo!

rows.label: tlk000501_02_msg0004
rows.name:
You don't need to worry about Nilny, mo!
Please, go quickly, mo!
